Package: triangdist
Title: Implementation of the Triangular Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("pacucam@alumni.uv.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions for the triangular distribution, 
    including density (dtriang), distribution (ptriang), quantile (qtriang), 
    and random generation (rtriang). It is fully vectorized and tested.
